                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>#34 to #46</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>0.6 &#177; 0.1 v</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>CI signal</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4" morerows="1">
                            <para>Less than .5v indicates an open between the ECM and IDM. 12 volts indicates an open in
                                the ECM or breakout box.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>#22 to #46</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
